4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge to become specialists in the field. The program spans 16 weeks, including three live online classes per week with a maximum of 16 participants. It covers essential skills such as Windows and Linux administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and risk management using strategies like data loss prevention. Students will also learn to navigate international compliance standards, including ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, participants receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. The classes are available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop